{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"23633-homeless-child","title":"Ikoku yen Emameotor Ere.","description":"Ikamunit ikoku yeni emametor ere lo iboio","language":"Ateso","langCode":"teo","isRtl":false,"level":"3","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Acaro Ruth"],"illustrators":["Avishek Sen","Greystroke","Upamanyu  Bhattacharyya"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/23633-homeless-child"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/52022/size3/180e056f5dc7f005063a599f57236b35.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/52022/size6/180e056f5dc7f005063a599f57236b35.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/52019/size6/5be57cf668da4c4ccb078f4fbdeb9ce4.jpg","text":"Irimirimei ijo etaun kere,\nIdo omamei ibore yeni inyamaret.\nIwonganar da konye emamei itunganana\nyeni iyuni.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/52017/size6/fb916783d605e10db099cc288dba6439.jpg","text":"Ikon imunyelen lu etukunenete ichuk lu etawun kere.\nIdo akon amujalala cha naa itani akonye itunga!\nIwomomoi ijo aparan kada akuware.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/52018/size6/4bea47ce0608f2d9a799e235c9cb5e3f.jpg","text":"Konye mam akon ariebo edmuni abongokinet.\nNarai emamei ijo idio itunganani,\nEmamei ijo Toto,\nEmamei papa,\nAraida onach arai inach,\nNara emamei yeni iboiotor ijo!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":3,"words":62}}